casebody.data:
Teresa VINSON-DOPP, Personal Representative of the Estate of Helen M. Vinson, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
Timothy LYONS, Defendant,
and
Noble Forestry, Inc., Defendant-Appellee. SC: 157828
COA: 335283 Supreme Court of Michigan. January 16, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the February 27, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.

Cavanagh, J., did not participate due to her prior relationship with Garan Lucow Miller, P.C.
